A vintage 1950s-style illustration of a single wooden pencil being sharpened by an old-fashioned hand-crank pencil sharpener on a worn oak desk, with curling wood shavings scattered artfully around. The scene is bathed in warm amber light from a nearby window, casting long shadows. In the background, a stack of crisp white paper awaits. The color palette features muted browns, creams, and soft golden yellows, with subtle paper texture overlay giving the entire image an aged, nostalgic quality reminiscent of mid-century magazine advertisements.
